WEBVTT

00:03:28.528 --> 00:03:33.441
And if you believe that my empathy
is directed towards you,

00:03:33.465 --> 00:03:35.692
you are far more likely to trust me.

00:03:36.303 --> 00:03:39.104
When all three
of these things are working,

00:03:39.128 --> 00:03:41.247
we have great trust.

00:03:42.165 --> 00:03:45.539
But if any one of these three gets shaky,

00:03:45.563 --> 00:03:49.188
if any one of these three wobbles,

00:03:49.212 --> 00:03:50.648
trust is threatened.

00:03:52.291 --> 00:03:54.047
Now here's what I'd like to do.

00:03:54.071 --> 00:03:59.228
I want each of us to be able
to engender more trust tomorrow,

00:03:59.252 --> 00:04:01.744
literally tomorrow, than we do today.